room_title: Escape room "Mystery of the Black Dahlia" by Escape Cocoa Beach in Melbourne
room_address: 5675 N Atlantic Ave Unit 113/114 Cocoa Beach, FL 32931
room_description:
One of America's oldest and most notorious cold cases involved the murder of a beautiful, young, aspiring actress near Hollywood, California. There were many persons of interest and a handful of serious suspects. No murder weapon(s) were ever located. The body had been severed at the waist along with many other disturbing injuries requiring surgical precision.
Stepping back in time, it's your job to enter the study of the lead suspect, a well-known local Dr. to the Hollywood elite. Can you find and recover the instruments used to commit this grizzly crime?
